{"id": 1772, "date": "1987-01-16T11:00:13", "date_gmt": "1987-01-16T19:00:13", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=1772"}, "modified": "2026-06-03T17:32:35", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-04T00:32:35", "slug": "matr-mick-jagger-little-richard-tina-turner-paul-simon-bruce-springsteen-et-al-bony-moronie", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1987/01/16/matr-mick-jagger-little-richard-tina-turner-paul-simon-bruce-springsteen-et-al-bony-moronie/", "title": {"rendered": "Bony Moronie"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>On January 18, 1989, Bruce joined an all-star jam band at the fourth annual Rock and Roll Hall of Fame induction ceremony. Included in the set: Larry Williams&#8217; 1957 hit, &#8220;Bony Moronie.&#8221;</p>\n<p>Bruce can only be seen and heard on guitar in the newly uploaded video below, but since it&#8217;s the only known recorded instance of him playing it, I&#8217;m sharing and including it here.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xeE2qLJJyXU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>It&#8217;s a more frenetic performance than the Larry Williams performance; see below for comparison.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mdmuqYCf5Ik?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>Bony Maronie<br />\nFirst performed:</strong> January 18, 1989 (New York City, NY)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> July 2, 1989 (Long Branch, NJ)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 April 27, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>New video: Bruce joins an all-start jam at the fourth annual Rock and Roll Hall of Fame and covers Larry Williams&#8217; &#8220;Bony Maronie.&#8221;</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 69668, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false}, "categories": [3617, 5], "tags": [869, 157, 868, 261, 870, 670, 727], "class_list": ["post-1772", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-it-takes-two", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-bony-moronie", "tag-hall-of-fame", "tag-larry-williams", "tag-little-richard", "tag-mick-jagger", "tag-paul-simon", "tag-tina-turner"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/est